{"ja436:0.1":"Jataka ","ja436:0.2":"Navakanipata ","ja436:0.3":"Gijjhavagga ","ja436:0.4":"10. Samuggajataka ","ja436:1.1":"“Kuto nu agacchatha bho tayo jana, ","ja436:1.2":"Svagata etha nisidathasane; ","ja436:1.3":"Kaccittha bhonto kusalam anamayam, ","ja436:1.4":"Cirassamabbhagamanam hi vo idha”. ","ja436:2.1":"“Ahameva eko idha majja patto, ","ja436:2.2":"Na capi me dutiyo koci vijjati; ","ja436:2.3":"Kimeva sandhaya te bhasitam ise, ","ja436:2.4":"‘Kuto nu agacchatha bho tayo jana’”. ","ja436:3.1":"“Tuvanca eko bhariya ca te piya, ","ja436:3.2":"Samuggapakkhittanikinnamantare; ","ja436:3.3":"Sa rakkhita kucchigatava te sada, ","ja436:3.4":"Vayussa puttena saha tahim rata”. ","ja436:4.1":"“Samviggarupo isina viyakato, ","ja436:4.2":"So danavo tattha samuggamuggili; ","ja436:4.3":"Addakkhi bhariyam suci maladharinim, ","ja436:4.4":"Vayussa puttena saha tahim ratam”. ","ja436:5.1":"“Sudittharupamuggatapanuvattina, ","ja436:5.2":"Hina nara ye pamadavasam gata; ","ja436:5.3":"Yatha have panarivettha rakkhita, ","ja436:5.4":"Duttha mayi annamabhippamodayi. ","ja436:6.1":"Diva ca ratto ca maya upatthita, ","ja436:6.2":"Tapassina jotiriva vane vasam; ","ja436:6.3":"Sa dhammamukkamma adhammamacari, ","ja436:6.4":"Akiriyarupo pamadahi santhavo. ","ja436:7.1":"Sariramajjhamhi thitatimannaham, ","ja436:7.2":"Mayham ayanti asatim asannatam; ","ja436:7.3":"Sa dhammamukkamma adhammamacari, ","ja436:7.4":"Akiriyarupo pamadahi santhavo. ","ja436:8.1":"Surakkhitam meti katham nu vissase, ","ja436:8.2":"Anekacittasu na hatthi rakkhana; ","ja436:8.3":"Eta hi patalapapatasannibha, ","ja436:8.4":"Etthappamatto byasanam nigaccha”ti. ","ja436:9.1":"“Tasma hi te sukhino vitasoka, ","ja436:9.2":"Ye matugamehi caranti nissata; ","ja436:9.3":"Etam sivam uttamamabhipatthayam, ","ja436:9.4":"Na matugamehi kareyya santhavanti”. ","ja436:10.1":"Samuggajatakam dasamam. "}